Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.30,0:28:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這個多少罩杯的? 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.84,0:28:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.21,0:28:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.11,0:28:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,想我摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.05,0:29:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧 舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.80,0:29:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很想做啊 欲求不滿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.14,0:29:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下面呢?   不行啊
